1566
01:31:11,291 --> 01:31:12,166
Sim, senhor.

1567
01:31:12,250 --> 01:31:13,916
Vá até lá e pergunta pela Rimjhim.

1568
01:31:14,000 --> 01:31:15,291
Me ligue quando encontrá-la.

1569
01:31:15,750 --> 01:31:17,041
