1598
01:32:56,833 --> 01:32:57,750
Vamos.

1599
01:32:58,791 --> 01:32:59,958
- Táxi?
- Sim, senhor?

1600
01:33:00,041 --> 01:33:01,416
- Está disponível?
- Com certeza.

1601
01:33:02,458 --> 01:33:03,875
Pegue a via do pedágio!

1602
01:33:05,083 --> 01:33:07,041
